meta.description: Gnome terminal emulator with support for tiling and tabs.
meta.name: gnome-terminator

meta.description: Terminal emulator with support for tiling and tabs
meta.long_description:
The goal of this project is to produce a useful tool for arranging
terminals. It is inspired by programs such as gnome-multi-term,
quadkonsole, etc. in that the main focus is arranging terminals in grids
(tabs is the most common default method, which Terminator also supports).
meta.name: gnome-terminator
